# üó∫Ô∏è FinMind Project Roadmap (2025-2026)

This roadmap outlines the development and research phases for the FinMind platform.

### **Phase 1: Foundation (Current)**
* [x] Initialize GitHub repository and project structure.
* [x] Develop basic Python recommendation logic.
* [x] Create initial Financial Literacy Hub.

### **Phase 2: Development (Next 2 Months)**
* [ ] Build a front-end interface using **Bubble** or **JavaScript**.
* [ ] Connect **Firebase** for secure, anonymous data storage.
* [ ] Expand the Finance Hub with videos and interactive calculators.

### **Phase 3: The Pilot Study (3-5 Months Out)**
* [ ] Recruit 30-50 high school student volunteers.
* [ ] Launch the "Beta" version of the platform.
* [ ] Collect and analyze engagement data to measure stress reduction.

### **Phase 4: Analysis & Application (Summer/Fall 2025)**
* [ ] Use **Python** (Pandas/Matplotlib) to visualize pilot data.
* [ ] Present findings in college application essays and portfolios.
